{"tid":1967713,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【榮恩做老竇】路柏格連特宣佈女友Georgia陀B","createTime":"2020-04-11T06:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T07:18:24.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"619c60c0ad506170e23053866832ab246be073a3","tid":1967713,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T06:38:29.000Z","msg":"在電影《哈利波特》（Harry Potter）系列飾演榮恩的英國男星路柏格連特（Rupert Grint）快將做老竇，與他拍拖多年的演員女友Georgia Groome宣佈陀B，兩人昨日透過發言人公佈喜訊：「路柏格連特和Georgia Groome很興奮地宣佈兩人正期待着BB的來臨，希望給予私人空間。」<br />\n<br />\nBB是兩人的第一胎，他們於2011年撻着，拍拖九年，Georgia演出2008年喜劇電影《Angus, Thongs and Perfect Snogging》後為人所熟悉。其實，Georgia前日就已經被影到大住肚與路柏在倫敦外出掃貨，近期武漢肺炎嚴重，兩人不但未有自我隔離，出街還沒有戴上口罩。Georgia去年亦被影得無名指戴上戒指後傳出婚訊，但一直都未有公佈結婚消息。<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20200411/large/1586575178_8cfb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200411%2Flarge%2F1586575178_8cfb.jpg&h=6c647163&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200411/M3DBOQWW7U4P4YA55CCIXM2H2Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200411%2FM3DBOQWW7U4P4YA55CCIXM2H2Y%2F&d=PwmYTnxQQ9jzt6ozq479VUUPjIZJXyGGplxIPwZjN5A%3D&h=0f0185a1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200411%2FM3DBOQWW7U4P4YA55CCIXM2H2Y%2F&h=5e8727ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200411/M3DBOQWW7U4P4YA55CCIXM2H2Y/</a>"},{"pid":"7dfd860c68856f586eff5a7c0fcd26e700b5f743","tid":1967713,"uid":137451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T06:45:59.000Z","msg":"真係唔撚識死 仲敢唔戴口罩周圍去 無腦"},{"pid":"646616b3ffd58012b8d76ed188647d10cf2ccb8e","tid":1967713,"uid":299372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T07:18:24.000Z","msg":"細個好鍾意佢<img src=